# FLEX

[![Build
Status](https://travis-ci.org/pipermerriam/flex.png)](https://travis-ci.org
/pipermerriam/flex)
[![Documentation
Status](https://readthedocs.org/projects/flex-swagger/badge/?version=latest
)](https://readthedocs.org/projects/flex-swagger/?badge=latest)
[![PyPi
version](https://img.shields.io/pypi/v/flex.svg)](https://pypi.python.org/p
ypi/flex)
[![PyPi
downloads](https://img.shields.io/pypi/dm/flex.svg)](https://pypi.python.or
g/pypi/flex)


Validation tooling for [Swagger
2.0](https://github.com/wordnik/swagger-spec/blob/master/versions/2.0.md)
specifications.


[Documentation on
ReadTheDocs](http://flex-swagger.readthedocs.org/en/latest/)

## Features

* Validate swagger schemas.
* JSON Schema Validation
* Validation of request/response objects against schema.
* Command Line interface.


# CLI Name Change

Starting in version 5.0.0 the CLI interface has been changed to
`swagger-flex`
due to a collission with the Apache Flex project.



